sql_text: SELECT { [Measures].[Order Quantity] }  ON COLUMNS,  SUBSET( Hierarchize(  { Union( { [Product Dimension].[Product Dimension].[Product Name].Members} , {[Product Dimension].[Product Dimension].[All]}) }   )  , 0, 50000) DIMENSION PROPERTIES HIERARCHY_UNIQUE_NAME, PARENT_UNIQUE_NAME ON ROWS FROM [internet_sales]

SELECT
{ [Measures].[Order Quantity] }  ON COLUMNS,
  SUBSET( Hierarchize(
  { Union( { [Product Dimension].[Product Dimension].[Product Name].Members} ,
  {[Product Dimension].[Product Dimension].[All]}) }
  )  , 0, 50000)
  DIMENSION PROPERTIES HIERARCHY_UNIQUE_NAME, PARENT_UNIQUE_NAME ON ROWS
  FROM [internet_sales]
